OL,3,CGuernsey cliff path steps to reopen
OL,4,Cafter a four-year closure
OL,6,FThe Clarence Battery steps in Guernsey
OL,7,Fare formally reopening after being
OL,8,Fclosed for four years.
OL,10,FThe States of Guernsey shut it in
OL,11,FMarch 2020 after heavy rain caused a
OL,12,Flandslip, covering the pathway.
OL,14,FAfter seven months of work
OL,15,Fcommissioned by the Environment &
OL,16,FInfrastructure Committee (E&I), the
OL,17,Fsteps once again link Guernsey's east
OL,18,Fand south coastal cliff paths.
