OL,3,CGuernsey cliff path steps to reopen
OL,4,Cafter a four-year closure
OL,6,FWork mainly involved stabilising the
OL,7,Frock faces and restoring the steps to
OL,8,Fa usable condition.
OL,10,FThe States also cleared the edges of
OL,11,Fthe stairs and leveled surfaces to
OL,12,Fimprove accessibility.
OL,14,FAn improved drainage system is now in
OL,15,Fplace to lower the risk of another
OL,16,Flandslip in the future.
OL,18,FDespite some minor ongoing works such
OL,19,Fas tree planting, the States has
OL,20,Freassured islanders that everything
OL,21,Fsubstantial is complete.
