OL,3,CGuernsey cliff path steps to reopen
OL,4,Cafter a four-year closure
OL,6,FE&I President, Deputy Lindsay de
OL,7,FSausmarez, will reopen the steps at
OL,8,F1:15pm on Friday 6 September.
OL,10,FShe explains: "We really are delighted
OL,11,Fto be able to complete this major
OL,12,Fproject and reopen these steps, which
OL,13,FI'm sure will be welcomed by islanders
OL,14,Fand visitors alike.
OL,16,F"While some will have seen seven
OL,17,Fmonths of visible works on site, this
OL,18,Fwas really the culmination of an
OL,19,Fintricate and detailed project to make
OL,20,Fthe area safe and get these steps back
OL,21,Fin action."
